## DESCRIPTION
## Michigan precalculus gateway problem: lines
## ENDDESCRIPTION

DOCUMENT();
loadMacros(
  "PGstandard.pl",
  "PGchoicemacros.pl",
  "MathObjects.pl",
  "contextFraction.pl",
  "PGcourse.pl"
);

Context("Fraction");

($a, $b, $c) = (2..13)[NchooseK(12,3)];

$ans = Compute("$a/$c");

Context()->texStrings;
BEGIN_TEXT

The \(y\)-intercept of the line having equation \($b x = $a - $c y\) is
\{ $ans->ans_rule(10) \}

END_TEXT
Context()->normalStrings;

ANS( $ans->cmp() );

Context()->texStrings;
SOLUTION(EV3(<<'END_SOLUTION'));
$PAR SOLUTION $PAR

The \(y\)-intercept occurs when \(x=0\), so we have
\[ $a - $c y = 0, \qquad\mbox{or}\qquad y = $ans.\]


END_SOLUTION
Context()->normalStrings;

ENDDOCUMENT();
